---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="SocialProof vs Squarespace Reviews — Dedicated Testimonial Tool vs Built-in | SocialProof"
  description="Does Squarespace's built-in review block do enough? See how SocialProof compares as a dedicated testimonial collection and display tool."
>
  <main class="vs-page">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">SocialProof vs Squarespace (built-in)</p>
        <h1>Squarespace has a review block. We're built for testimonials.</h1>
        <div class="cta-group">
          <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn btn-primary">Try SocialProof free</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="intro">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="lead">Squarespace has a built-in reviews feature, but it's designed for product reviews on commerce sites — not for collecting and curating customer testimonials for service businesses. SocialProof is purpose-built for that use case: send a collect link, approve submissions, embed anywhere — including in your Squarespace site.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="comparison-table">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Feature comparison</h2>
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Feature</th>
              <th>Squarespace (built-in)</th>
              <th>SocialProof</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>Collect reviews via shareable link</td><td>❌ Customers must visit your Squarespace site</td><td>✅ Send a link anywhere (text, email, QR)</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Works for service businesses</td><td>⚠️ Primarily product-focused</td><td>✅ Yes — built for service businesses</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Works without a Squarespace site</td><td>❌ Squarespace only</td><td>✅ Any website or no website</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Custom intake form fields</td><td>❌ Limited</td><td>✅ Yes — name, role, company, custom questions</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Approve/reject before publishing</td><td>⚠️ Limited moderation</td><td>✅ Full moderation dashboard</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Star ratings + written testimonials</td><td>✅ Yes</td><td>✅ Yes</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Export testimonials</td><td>❌ Platform-locked</td><td>✅ Yes — export anytime</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Free tier</td><td>Included in Squarespace plan</td><td>✅ Free forever for 1 active widget</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Price</td><td>Included in $16-$52+/mo Squarespace plans</td><td>$9/mo Pro</td></tr>

          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="verdict">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>The honest verdict</h2>
        <p>If you're already on Squarespace and only need basic product reviews, the built-in block might be fine. If you're a service business who wants to collect testimonials via a shareable link, moderate them, and display them in a polished widget — SocialProof is built for you.</p>
        <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn btn-primary">Start free — no credit card</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
